  <summary date="2017-03-30T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Employer Participation in Repayment Act of 2017

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the tax exclusion for employer-provided educational assistance to include an employer's payments to an employee or lender for the principal or interest on any qualified education loan incurred by an employee.</summary>
